SERVICES
Description of the Services
The App is a Beat making learning tool, that enables you to learn and play on a drum-pad like interface and to create content (“User Content”), by yourself or based on MWM Content and to share it.
The App offers in particular the following functionalities:
Creating your User Account
Creating and recording User Content;
Downloading and sharing your User Content;
Using MWM Contents;
Consulting these Terms of Use.
If you subscribe to the Premium Services, the App will be free from any advertising, and you may have access to the following additional functionalities:
get unlimited access to the Premium songs catalog,
play with all instruments available in the App.
Price of the Services - Premium Services
The access to the App and to the Services are entirely free of charge, except for the Premium Services.
You may subscribe to the Premium Services directly on the App, through the App Store or Google Play.
The subscriptions we offer are renewed tacitly weekly, monthly or yearly, depending on the subscription you have chosen. If you wish to cancel your subscription, you must do it through Apple or Google at least 24 hours before the next invoicing date (see in particular: https://support.apple.com/HT202039). If you cancel your subscription, you will still be able to use the Premium Services features until the expiry of your subscription. All fees paid in advance are acquired by MWM, and you will in no case be refunded pro-rata for the time left on your subscription.
You are informed that MWM reserves the right to change the subscription plans, or adjust their pricing, in any manner and at any time. Any price changes or changes to your subscription plan will take effect after a reasonable notice period.
Unless otherwise allowed through the Apple Store or Google Play, in accordance with article L121-21-8, 13° of the French Consumer Code, you are informed, that when subscribing to the Premium Services, you expressly accept that the performance of the contract begins at the time of your purchase, and waive your right of withdrawal.
The cost of connecting to the Internet, and other fees relating to telecommunications are entirely your own responsibility.
