The first time you connect on the App, a pop up will be displayed, informing you that if you give your consent, your advertising ID (IDFA) and other data, such as location data, and other demographic and interest data about you will be transmitted to MoPub, a division of Twitter, and all its data partners, and Appsflyer for the purpose of providing you with a personalized advertising experience. You are free to refuse or agree to such processing.
